  <brief_title>&quot;Score Infectivity&quot; During Reoperation on Total Hip or Knee Prosthesis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Definition of a &quot;Score Infectivity&quot; During Reoperation on Total Hip or Knee Prosthesis</official_title>
